1
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,280
I'm making you
vice president of our company.

2
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,600
You mean it, Dad?

3
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:45,880
Keep your eyes on everyone
in the Chokprasertsap family.

4
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,600
That's your old family name, isn't it?

5
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:50,560
These are the names of the suspects
and several persons of interest.

6
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,960
And if what you're thinking
turns out to be true,

7
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,480
what will you do?

8
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,600
Then it'll be to the death.

9
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,640
He can hurt me and I'll take it.

10
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:01,440
But when he hurts you,
the person I love most,

11
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,960
I can't forgive that.

12
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,160
Boss.

13
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,800
Tawan.

14
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,840
You're here early. Have you eaten yet?

15
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,160
Why come here and ruin the mood?

16
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,560
Hey.

17
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:34,000
- Hey!
- Tawan!

18
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,640
How dare you slap my son!

19
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:41,200
Then ask your son first

20
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,680
how he could do such an evil thing.

21
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,880
What are you talking about?

22
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:54,120
Mr. Mekha, please come with us
to the station to give a statement.

23
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,320
Hold on, officer.

24
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:02,640
What has my son done
that you're taking him in?

25
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,800
Tawan, why did you call the police?

26
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:07,640
What lies are you feeding them about me?

27
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:10,400
Your subordinate,
Mr. Thawat, has confessed.

28
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:13,280
He testified that you ordered him

29
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,720
to abduct Ms. Ayla, daughter of Mr. Thana,

30
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:18,680
to force Mr. Thana
to withdraw from the bidding.

31
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:29,760
And in the incident, one of Mr. Thana's
hired bodyguards was killed.

32
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,560
But I didn't order that.

33
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:39,160
Dad, you've got to believe me.

34
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,840
Thawat acted on his own.

35
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:43,640
I know nothing about it.

36
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,760
I'm not involved in any of it!

37
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,960
Dad…

38
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:55,040
Mom… Please help me, Mom.

39
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:58,400
Of course, I'll help you. Calm down.
They're framing you.

40
00:03:58,480 --> 00:03:59,880
That bitch is framing you!

41
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,520
You've got to help our son.

42
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,600
Please come with us.

43
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:13,080
Mom! Mom, help me!

44
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,960
I didn't do it, officer!

45
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,399
Let me go! I'm innocent!

46
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,640
- Mom! Mom!
- Mek!

47
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,200
- You have to help him!
- Mom!

48
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,519
- You have to!
- Let me go!

49
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,120
He didn't do anything wrong!

50
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,520
Don't just believe one side of the story.

51
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,400
You have to help him!

52
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,640
Mek, my son! Mek!

53
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,720
Mek!

54
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:04,520
That girl… She's safe, isn't she?

55
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,360
Ayla's safe.

56
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,440
Good…

57
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,000
That's good.

58
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,360
Hey!

59
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:28,120
How could you just stand there
and do nothing?

60
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:31,920
How could you let them
drag our son away like that?

61
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,400
The police have the evidence.

62
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,800
Are you going to say our son's innocent?

63
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:39,480
Stop spoiling him the wrong way.

64
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,360
Spoiling him?

65
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,680
You're saying I'm the one spoiling him?

66
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:47,240
You've never once

67
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:49,080
taken his side!

68
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:52,840
Everything Mek does,
to you, is wrong, bad, worthless.

69
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:55,840
Nothing he does
is ever good enough for you.

70
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,320
The only one who pleases you…

71
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:05,240
Is that mistress's daughter. Everything
she does is perfect in your eyes!

72
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,080
That's why, isn't it?

73
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:10,440
That's why
you're letting our son rot in jail!

74
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:13,040
Listen to me. I've never played favorites.

75
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,400
I love both my children the same.

76
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,560
You're the one who hates Tawan.

77
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,840
And you poisoned Mek into hating her too.

78
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:24,280
In the end, they could never
live under the same roof.

79
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,120
So, this is my fault?

80
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:31,040
You destroyed their bond.

81
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,000
The elder hates the younger.

82
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,960
The younger rejects the elder.

83
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,560
How fortunate

84
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:42,840
you haven't turned Mek against me as well.

85
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,640
I'll tell you this.

86
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,920
If Mek ends up in prison,

87
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:55,040
both he and I will hate you
for the rest of our lives.

88
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,480
Couldn't sleep?

89
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,560
Because of your father?

90
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,840
This is the first time

91
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,360
I've seen his tears.

92
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:53,080
I understand.

93
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,600
I don't know

94
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:10,520
how much this will break him.

95
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,720
Mek's case

96
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:21,600
could shake the board of directors,

97
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:25,000
destroy the company's credibility.

98
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:29,800
If Dad can't fix this problem,

99
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:36,159
then there might not be
a T.S. Construction anymore.

100
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:56,520
Mr. Mek's case looks grim.

101
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,880
The evidence is solid.

102
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:03,320
Multiple money transfer slips
from him to the suspect,

103
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:05,600
especially on the day of the abduction.

104
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,000
The total is in the millions.

105
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:13,440
Can we at least apply for bail?

106
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,320
It's going to be very difficult.

107
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,720
Draft the termination papers
for the latest project.

108
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:30,000
If we cancel,
the penalty fees will be enormous.

109
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,920
No matter how much it costs, we'll pay.

110
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,480
Boss,

111
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:54,600
intel says T.S. Construction

112
00:09:54,680 --> 00:09:56,920
has pulled out of their latest project.

113
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:22,320
I think your father
must've thought it through

114
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:24,120
before deciding that.

115
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,720
T.S. CONSTRUCTION SECRETARY

116
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:58,560
Hello?

117
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:00,760
Hello, Ms. Tawan.

118
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:02,680
Hello.

119
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:06,280
Let me get straight to the point.

120
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:09,680
Ever since the incident with Mr. Mek,

121
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:11,720
Mr. Songklod
hasn't been functioning at all.

122
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:15,160
No partner meetings, no signing papers,

123
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,280
no site visits.

124
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:18,120
We don't know what to do anymore.

125
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:20,560
Ms. Duangnet stepped in to handle things,

126
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:24,400
but honestly, it's only gotten worse.

127
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:46,200
You had time to come see me today, huh?

128
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,240
What about you, Dad?

129
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,240
Not going in to work?

130
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:01,120
All I ever wanted
was to build this company

131
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:03,640
into the biggest in ASEAN,

132
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:07,840
for the future of both Mek and you.

133
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,840
Sometimes I wonder…

134
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:15,920
All this ambition,

135
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,440
all this fighting…

136
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,600
What's it really worth?

137
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:23,040
The wealth, the assets,

138
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:25,840
traded for family,

139
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,360
for friendships lost.

140
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:33,240
Was it worth it?

141
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:48,920
If I came to help at the company,

142
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,240
would you teach me the ropes?

143
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:01,880
Don't waste your time on a company
that's already on the brink of collapse.

144
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:23,280
I'd like you two

145
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:26,000
to design the third floor
so it goes with the rest of the building.

146
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:27,920
Please help look into this.

147
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:33,040
And you, please help
on the swimming pool design.

148
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,240
Please help handle this.

149
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,880
I'll help the company.

150
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:48,280
This here is our latest quarter report.

151
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:50,760
We're down 11.1%.

152
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:05,520
As for the industry outlook…

153
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:21,680
We were just discussing
the latest VIP client, Boss.

154
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:25,560
This project
is a 45-story residential tower.

155
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:28,320
The current design is twin towers.

156
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:40,520
If we can build new investor confidence,

157
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:43,560
we'll stand a chance
at winning government bids.

158
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:47,120
That could restore
the company's liquidity.

159
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:49,040
I agree.

160
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,760
I agree as well.

161
00:15:04,640 --> 00:15:05,960
Yes?

162
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:07,280
Hello, Tawan.

163
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:10,720
On your way home yet? I'm about to sleep.

164
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:13,040
Not yet. Still working.

165
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:16,240
What, still not done?

166
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:18,640
Have you even eaten?

167
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:21,000
I had a sandwich.

168
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:23,760
Just trying to clear this backlog.

169
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:28,040
Might be a late night.

170
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:32,280
First day and already
working hard, Ms. CEO.

171
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:38,280
What about you? How was your day?

172
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:40,760
Tired?

173
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:44,800
Not at all. At this level, it's a breeze.

174
00:15:45,640 --> 00:15:48,400
You're not upset with me, right?

175
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:50,680
For not picking you up?

176
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:54,080
Not at all. I understand

177
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:56,880
why you're doing this.

178
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:59,560
I won't sulk. I'm grown up now.

179
00:16:00,280 --> 00:16:03,320
My girlfriend is the sweetest.

180
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,640
Then I won't bother you anymore.

181
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:08,200
Get back to work.

182
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,440
Goodnight,

183
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,680
my love.

184
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:20,280
Goodnight.

185
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:22,720
Love you most.

186
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:49,640
Mr. Thana, I sincerely apologize

187
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:53,280
for the awful things my brother did to you

188
00:16:53,920 --> 00:16:55,120
and Ayla.

189
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:00,960
The matter's now

190
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:03,720
in the hands of the law.

191
00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:07,079
And where's Songklod hiding?

192
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:10,240
Why are you apologizing for him?

193
00:17:12,319 --> 00:17:13,800
Make him kneel before me!

194
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:16,520
What kind of man raises a son that vile?

195
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:21,079
I'm speaking on behalf
of my father and our family.

196
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:23,680
But I assure you,

197
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:26,400
he had no knowledge

198
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:29,960
or involvement in what my brother did.

199
00:17:33,040 --> 00:17:34,080
And how can you be so sure

200
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:37,960
he wasn't involved?

201
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:41,160
If he had been,

202
00:17:43,840 --> 00:17:47,400
he wouldn't have canceled
our latest project contract,

203
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:51,920
costing the company tens of millions.

204
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:59,080
He feels devastated by what happened.

205
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:03,800
Even the company
he built with his own hands,

206
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:06,960
he was willing to let it collapse.

207
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:15,720
What is it you really want from me?

208
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:19,800
I know I can't ask you

209
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:22,880
to forgive my father.

210
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:27,320
But I stand by what I said before.

211
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:32,080
I will take care of Ayla
and protect her for the rest of my life.

212
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:39,480
I only hope my sincerity and my life itself

213
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:43,000
might at least begin
to make amends for the failures

214
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:47,240
of the Chokprasertsap family.

215
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:15,080
Songklod is lucky

216
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:18,120
to have you as his daughter.

217
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:35,800
I'm so glad

218
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:39,360
that this time,
Dad has forgiven your father too.

219
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:46,440
They must know each other well enough.

220
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:50,600
So Mr. Thana believes
my father truly had no part in it.

221
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,720
The two of them…

222
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:58,720
They were best friends once. Why fight?

223
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:00,880
And drag the children into it?

224
00:20:06,760 --> 00:20:09,160
If it weren't for all this bad blood,

225
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:12,560
we might've met long ago.

226
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,320
Oh!

227
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:16,920
You're right!

228
00:20:18,360 --> 00:20:21,040
I could've met you back in grade school.

229
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:22,280
What a shame.

230
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:26,760
No. Kindergarten!

231
00:20:26,840 --> 00:20:28,200
Kindergarten?

232
00:20:28,280 --> 00:20:30,560
Or maybe in Mommy's womb.

233
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:37,640
Well, even if we met late,
we still found each other.

234
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:40,520
Then here's my promise.

235
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,440
No matter when or where,

236
00:20:44,360 --> 00:20:46,840
I'll keep finding you, in every lifetime.

237
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:50,840
You'll never escape me.

238
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:03,680
And I'll gladly let you find me.

239
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:55,760
I'm afraid Mr. Mek's case is hopeless.

240
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:43,080
Take the bags to the car.

241
00:22:49,600 --> 00:22:50,720
Congratulations.

242
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:55,360
You got everything you wanted.

243
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:57,040
The company,

244
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:59,840
your father, this house.

245
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:02,520
By working instead of Dad,

246
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,480
I'm not taking advantage.

247
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:07,360
And I'm not trying
to steal anything from anyone.

248
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:11,360
I'm only doing

249
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:12,960
what any daughter should.

250
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:21,320
You're doing it well.

251
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:24,600
When Mek returns,

252
00:23:26,040 --> 00:23:28,640
I'll hand everything back to him.

253
00:23:36,160 --> 00:23:37,160
Everything.

254
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:43,320
You know me. I keep my word.

255
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,640
This house

256
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:48,000
belongs to Father,

257
00:23:48,001 --> 00:24:19,835
Officail Website : 📺 dramacool.club

258
00:24:19,859 --> 00:24:48,155
Translate by =Qari= @Team Viki

259
00:23:48,080 --> 00:23:49,480
to you,

260
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:51,480
to Mek.

261
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:54,280
But not to me.

262
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:33,840
Tawan.

263
00:24:38,760 --> 00:24:40,560
I brought some papers for you to sign.

264
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:44,000
Papers?

265
00:24:45,840 --> 00:24:47,200
Actually,

266
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:49,320
Mr. Tos asked for your signature.

267
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:56,200
I'm helping at the company now, Dad.

268
00:24:58,120 --> 00:24:59,120
Why?

269
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:03,200
Because I don't want to see
everything fall apart.

270
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:16,200
Yesterday I met with Mr. Thana.

271
00:25:20,080 --> 00:25:22,080
He said

272
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:25,480
this time, he'll forgive you.

273
00:25:30,080 --> 00:25:32,160
And he asked me to tell you,

274
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:35,400
he hopes

275
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:38,640
you'll finally reflect

276
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:41,000
and learn something.

277
00:25:47,760 --> 00:25:49,120
That bastard!

278
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:57,480
Thank you, my child.

279
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:01,720
Thank you so much.

280
00:26:08,520 --> 00:26:10,120
All this time

281
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:13,560
I've been a terrible father.

282
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:16,480
I never protected you,
never took care of you.

283
00:26:16,560 --> 00:26:19,600
I let you suffer alone.

284
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:23,840
And because I didn't want you
fighting with Mek anymore,

285
00:26:25,520 --> 00:26:27,800
I forced myself
to send you away to Hong Kong.

286
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:33,760
At least there,
your aunt and uncle could keep you safe.

287
00:26:39,520 --> 00:26:42,160
Mui, I'm entrusting my daughter to you.

288
00:26:43,520 --> 00:26:46,160
I can't bear to see her
living like this anymore.

289
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:48,960
Duangnet has gone too far.

290
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:53,600
I never realized
how much Tawan was suffering.

291
00:26:54,720 --> 00:26:56,240
When will you send her?

292
00:26:57,360 --> 00:26:58,400
Tomorrow.

293
00:26:59,760 --> 00:27:01,080
Please, take care of her.

294
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,200
Tawan,

295
00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:16,520
go live with Aunt Mui in Hong Kong, okay?

296
00:28:04,040 --> 00:28:05,400
You know, Tawan,

297
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:11,960
you've always been my pride.

298
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:19,240
Even when you refused to see me

299
00:28:19,320 --> 00:28:21,400
during my visits,

300
00:28:25,360 --> 00:28:26,520
I knew

301
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:29,240
how hard you were studying.

302
00:28:30,280 --> 00:28:31,720
I knew your dreams.

303
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:45,640
It's in the past, Dad.

304
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:47,880
Please don't say more.

305
00:28:55,760 --> 00:28:56,880
I'm sorry.

306
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:02,320
Sorry.

307
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:05,960
I never looked after you.

308
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:09,120
Sorry I made you suffer.

309
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:14,000
Please give me one more chance.

310
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:41,280
Thank you, my child.

311
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:44,120
Thank you so much.

312
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:19,560
And your dad's not going
to kick me out of the house?

313
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:23,800
I'm right here.

314
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:26,480
You don't have to be afraid of anything.

315
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,800
Hello, Aa.

316
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:53,240
I'm Ayla.

317
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:56,480
I brought you lots of vitamins today.

318
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:03,080
Not Aa.

319
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:05,600
Call me Lung, like Uncle.

320
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:10,160
I'm older than your father
by a few months.

321
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:19,480
Thank you. Sit down.

322
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:29,320
That day we first met… I'm sorry.

323
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:31,120
I spoke harshly to you.

324
00:31:32,120 --> 00:31:33,680
It's okay.

325
00:31:33,760 --> 00:31:35,760
I understood the situation.

326
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:37,600
And honestly, my dad

327
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:39,400
wasn't exactly gentle either.

328
00:31:42,800 --> 00:31:44,040
The truth is…

329
00:31:46,040 --> 00:31:49,000
It was me who cheated your father.

330
00:31:55,760 --> 00:31:58,640
Back then, we started
a construction company together.

331
00:31:59,280 --> 00:32:02,520
We were best friends and partners.

332
00:32:04,360 --> 00:32:06,640
But I got greedy. I wanted to get rich fast.

333
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:09,480
So, I secretly set up my own company.

334
00:32:10,080 --> 00:32:12,680
And when I found out
how much Thana would bid,

335
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:16,440
I always undercut him to win.

336
00:32:18,360 --> 00:32:21,280
In the end, the company
we built together collapsed.

337
00:32:24,080 --> 00:32:26,200
And I pulled out my shares
before it happened,

338
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:29,760
leaving your father
to shoulder all the debts,

339
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:31,480
to pay off employees,

340
00:32:31,560 --> 00:32:33,880
to pay the suppliers.

341
00:32:39,280 --> 00:32:40,760
I'm glad

342
00:32:42,360 --> 00:32:43,920
you finally admitted the truth.

343
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:50,320
The truth is the truth.

344
00:32:52,280 --> 00:32:54,720
And I also want to apologize for my son,

345
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:58,560
for the harm
he caused you and your father.

346
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,520
I truly regret it.

347
00:33:01,120 --> 00:33:03,000
Please don't blame yourself.

348
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:06,000
My father and I are safe now.

349
00:33:06,080 --> 00:33:09,040
And besides, Tawan takes good care of me.

350
00:33:14,560 --> 00:33:15,960
No wonder.

351
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,320
That's why she loves you so much.

352
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:45,760
You can't stop smiling.

353
00:33:48,960 --> 00:33:50,040
Of course.

354
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:54,200
I've already secured my crown
as the family's future daughter-in-law.

355
00:33:58,480 --> 00:34:00,880
And you can be sure

356
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:03,800
I've never given that title

357
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:05,400
to anyone else.

358
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:10,520
Let's get married then.

359
00:34:11,239 --> 00:34:12,239
I want to marry you.

360
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:19,000
Slow down, Ayla.

361
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:21,920
That line is supposed to come from me.

362
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:25,520
Oh please, whoever says it doesn't matter.
What matters is the result.

363
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:30,760
So? Are we getting married or not?

364
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:33,960
We are.

365
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:38,120
But Mr. Thana
won't storm our wedding, right?

366
00:34:38,719 --> 00:34:40,840
Oh, you just ruined the mood.

367
00:34:43,239 --> 00:34:45,159
Let's hope

368
00:34:46,239 --> 00:34:47,440
he softens his heart.

369
00:34:51,239 --> 00:34:52,440
Have hope!

370
00:34:52,520 --> 00:34:56,040
Have hope, have hope… I'm manifesting it!

371
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:58,720
Have hope, have hope, have hope!

372
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:08,560
Hope or not,

373
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:11,320
I'll never

374
00:35:13,160 --> 00:35:15,840
let go of the one

375
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:18,320
my heart chose.

376
00:35:39,120 --> 00:35:41,640
I love your treehouse, Tawan.

377
00:35:57,080 --> 00:35:58,600
So that means…

378
00:35:58,680 --> 00:36:00,840
The only one left is your dearest dad.

379
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:07,000
Honestly, it's not about Tawan.

380
00:36:07,080 --> 00:36:10,640
It's old grudges between our fathers.

381
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:12,600
I don't know
when they'll forgive each other.

382
00:36:12,680 --> 00:36:16,160
Well, at least now there's a little light
at the end of the tunnel.

383
00:36:17,040 --> 00:36:19,520
Just hoping that day comes soon.

384
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:25,120
BEC MUSIC FESTIVAL.

385
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:09,560
And…

386
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:11,640
Where's Tawan been?

387
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:12,840
I haven't seen her lately.

388
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:15,440
You miss her?

389
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:23,040
She's been busy,
working for both companies.

390
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:25,760
We only get to talk
on the phone these days.

391
00:37:27,240 --> 00:37:29,880
I've signed off on several payments

392
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:31,560
for her bodyguard services.

393
00:37:32,120 --> 00:37:34,000
But accounting tells me

394
00:37:34,640 --> 00:37:37,160
her company hasn't picked up the checks.

395
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:41,080
Tell her to come get them.

396
00:37:42,200 --> 00:37:44,360
She won't take them.

397
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:48,360
She says

398
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:52,280
protecting me is her duty
as a good girlfriend.

399
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:54,880
When she can't be here herself,
she sends her staff.

400
00:37:54,960 --> 00:37:56,640
The whole team.

401
00:37:56,720 --> 00:37:58,680
I'm basically.

402
00:37:58,760 --> 00:38:01,360
VVVVIP Ayla!

403
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:11,000
If only she weren't Songklod's daughter,

404
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,240
things would be so much easier.

405
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:17,960
But can't her goodness

406
00:38:18,040 --> 00:38:20,000
outweigh that or something?

407
00:38:21,240 --> 00:38:22,480
Time will tell.

408
00:38:24,120 --> 00:38:26,520
Let's wait and see.

409
00:38:26,600 --> 00:38:30,600
Then get ready, Dad. You'll be seeing
a lot of her for a very, very long time.

410
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:32,320
Because I'm not letting go.

411
00:38:56,680 --> 00:38:57,720
Tawan!

412
00:38:58,720 --> 00:39:00,880
Wait, how did you get here?
You said you couldn't come!

413
00:39:03,200 --> 00:39:04,360
Come here.

414
00:39:21,640 --> 00:39:22,960
Kie.

415
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:27,040
- It's…
- Oh, okay.

416
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:54,160
Actually, it'd be nice
if you could sit here and watch, clearly.

417
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:59,080
You really want me to just sit and watch?

418
00:39:59,680 --> 00:40:02,440
Don't you feel
it's a waste of my potential?

419
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:04,240
I'm a great bodyguard, you know.

420
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:07,760
So what? I just want to sing for you.

421
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:09,440
That's been my dream.

422
00:40:09,520 --> 00:40:11,880
If you sit here and listen to me sing,

423
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:14,480
and I'm singing right here…

424
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:18,280
But if you came up and sang with me,

425
00:40:18,880 --> 00:40:20,720
that would make me so happy.

426
00:40:24,560 --> 00:40:27,200
Me? On stage? Singing?

427
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:31,280
Poor audience.

428
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:34,360
Don't lie. I've heard you sing before.

429
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:36,160
I was eavesdropping.

430
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:41,200
You really are trouble.

431
00:40:43,640 --> 00:40:45,040
I'll stick to listening.

432
00:40:47,215 --> 00:41:18,968
Officail Website : 📺 dramacool.club

433
00:41:18,992 --> 00:41:47,215
Translate by =Qari= @Team Viki

434
00:40:49,240 --> 00:40:50,240
Fine, fine.

435
00:40:51,080 --> 00:40:53,880
I won't force you up on stage.

436
00:40:55,800 --> 00:40:57,240
But can I ask just one thing?

437
00:40:57,760 --> 00:41:00,360
Will you sit here
and watch over me while I'm singing?

438
00:41:06,760 --> 00:41:08,960
Tomorrow I have a big meeting.

439
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:11,360
A major project.

440
00:41:12,040 --> 00:41:13,360
I can't skip it.

441
00:41:15,400 --> 00:41:17,280
That's a shame.

442
00:41:19,200 --> 00:41:20,480
But I won't sulk.

443
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:23,400
I'm sorry.

444
00:41:24,160 --> 00:41:25,960
No, don't be.

445
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:29,000
You didn't do anything wrong.
Really, I understand.

446
00:41:29,080 --> 00:41:31,680
Just wish me luck. That's enough.

447
00:41:33,160 --> 00:41:35,520
My Ayla's amazing.

448
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:37,920
You've got this.

449
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:40,120
Piece of cake, right?

450
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:22,520
Is Tawan here yet?

451
00:42:24,960 --> 00:42:26,080
Not yet.

452
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:33,520
BACK STAGE STAFF ONLY

453
00:43:03,320 --> 00:43:07,080
I just wish
You'd understand my heart for once.

454
00:43:07,800 --> 00:43:13,520
Every time I lock eyes with you
I'm hoping you'll hear my voice.

455
00:43:13,600 --> 00:43:17,320
Hear what it's saying deep inside.

456
00:43:18,520 --> 00:43:22,760
But you never seem to care at all.

457
00:43:22,840 --> 00:43:26,520
No matter how hard I try.

458
00:43:26,600 --> 00:43:31,680
Your heart stays closed
And all you do is look right past me.

459
00:43:31,760 --> 00:43:36,280
You better know, the one you're looking at
Won't just fall for your magic like that.

460
00:43:36,360 --> 00:43:39,960
You better know, I'm a superstar.

461
00:43:40,040 --> 00:43:43,280
If you wanna try You'll
have to wait in line.

462
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:45,680
It's not that I'm stuck-up
I'm just not that easygoing.

463
00:43:45,760 --> 00:43:48,920
If you wanna shoot your shot
You'll have to pass my review.

464
00:43:50,400 --> 00:43:52,640
Only you.

465
00:43:52,720 --> 00:43:56,520
Don't mean to scare you…

466
00:44:25,400 --> 00:44:27,200
See you later!

467
00:44:27,280 --> 00:44:32,880
Encore! Encore!

468
00:44:32,960 --> 00:44:37,160
Encore! Encore!

469
00:44:50,800 --> 00:44:51,800
Ayla.

470
00:45:31,680 --> 00:45:33,040
How could this happen?

471
00:45:33,120 --> 00:45:34,520
Ayla is still so young.

472
00:45:34,600 --> 00:45:37,440
She won't be able to go back
to working the way she used to.

473
00:45:37,520 --> 00:45:39,360
Please tell me the truth.

474
00:45:40,400 --> 00:45:43,000
Is this your way of forcing me
to accept you,

475
00:45:43,680 --> 00:45:45,880
even as Songklod's daughter?

476
00:45:45,960 --> 00:45:48,600
Please just give me the chance
to see them one more time.

477
00:45:48,680 --> 00:45:50,480
Are you sure you can handle this, Ayla?

478
00:45:50,560 --> 00:45:53,160
Ayla! Ayla!

479
00:45:53,240 --> 00:45:56,840
I don't know if this will be
the last time we meet.

480
00:47:18,360 --> 00:47:20,920
Subtitles translation by: Praeploy Mahawan
